{
  "doc_id": "35016",
  "text": "CCO amino acid sequence alignments were carried out with Clustal Omega (69) and were annotated with Espript [CITATION_1] . Structural motifs involving specific amino acid sequences were identified and analyzed with PDBeMotif using the MSDmotif algorithm [CITATION_2] . Secondary structures and contact surfaces for the ACO/RPE65 chimera crystal structures were analyzed with PDBsum (30) and PISA [CITATION_3] . Electrostatics calculations were carried out with APBS [CITATION_4] . Figures displaying three-dimensional structures were rendered using PyMOL (Schrö dinger, LLC).",
